quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  101,1,The resurrection/disaster/calamity
  101,2,What (is) the resurrection/disaster/calamity
  101,3,And what made you know/informed you what the resurrection/disaster/calamity (is)
  101,4,"A day/time the people be/become like the butterflies, the scattered/ravished"
  101,5,"And the mountains be/become like the wool/dyed wool, the carded (ruffled)"
  101,6,So as for who his weights became heavy
  101,7,So he is in (an) acceptable/approved life/quality of life
  101,8,And but who his weights were reduced/lightened
  101,9,So his origin (is) Hell/destruction
  101,10,And what made you know/informed you what it is (E)
  101,11,hot fire